title: South Korea’s Coinone rocked by crypto listing bribery scandal
description: In a startling turn of events, a former executive at Coinone, one of South Korea's top cryptocurrency exchanges, has admitted to receiving bribes in return for listing specific cryptocurrencies on the platform.
